|1 |├─PX COORDINATOR           |        |4       |22          |
|2 |│ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|4       |21          |
|3 |│   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |4       |20          |
|4 |│     └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t3      |4       |20          |
|5 |└─PX COORDINATOR           |        |4       |24          |
|6 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX20000|4       |22          |
|7 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |4       |20          |
|8 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t4      |4       |20          |
===============================================================
